OL,3,CThe Windermere Children return to
OL,4,Cwhere they found sanctuary after WW2
OL,6,FA Holocaust survivor who arrived in
OL,7,Fthe Lake District alongside hundreds
OL,8,Fof other young people liberated from
OL,9,FNazi death camps, says they were
OL,10,F"miracle children."
OL,12,FEighty years ago, 300 child survivors
OL,13,Farrived at the former Calgarth Estate
OL,14,Fin Cumbria where they were given
OL,15,Fsanctuary and time to heal from the
OL,16,Fhorrors they'd endured.
OL,18,FTo mark the anniversary, some of the
OL,19,Fsurvivors and their relatives returned
OL,20,Fto the Lake District for a special
OL,21,Fevent.
