OL,3,CThe Windermere Children return to
OL,4,Cwhere they found sanctuary after WW2
OL,6,F"There was no provision for us because
OL,7,Fno one believed that young children
OL,8,Fwould survive - we were miracle
OL,9,Fchildren in a way.
OL,11,F"They wanted to separate us, like the
OL,12,Folder children. We thought, 'No, we're
OL,13,Fnot having this.' We'd been together
OL,14,Ffor two years... we were like one
OL,15,Fperson."
OL,17,FAustrian-born Jackie Young, aged 83,
OL,18,Fsays both of his parents were killed
OL,19,Fin Belarus, he said: "I only found out
OL,20,Ftwo years ago who my father was.
