OL,3,CThe Windermere Children return to
OL,4,Cwhere they found sanctuary after WW2
OL,6,F"My mother and father were on the same
OL,7,Ftransport to a place in Belarus... you
OL,8,Feither arrived dead in a gas van or
OL,9,Fyou were shot when you arrived.
OL,11,F"I thought I was just a regular North
OL,12,FLondon Jewish kid, then I got the
OL,13,Fshock at nine years old that I was
OL,14,Fadopted.
OL,16,F"My adopted grandmother told me that I
OL,17,Fwas from Austria, which came to me in
OL,18,Fmy teenage years. My life changed from
OL,19,Fthat time, searching for my past."
